How can I contact OpenSea?

Updated over 2 months ago

Were here to help! We provide agent support for all of our users in our Help Center, or by clicking the Support button on opensea.io. When you reach out to us, you'll be asked to provide:

  • Your email address

  • Your wallet address (Connect wallet if applicable)

  • Detailed information about your question or the issues you're experiencing

  • Verify Your NFT through contract

Sharing these details helps us address your concern as quickly and efficiently as possible.
